Kyle Secor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kyle_Secor 0 Kyle Ivan Secor (born May 31, 1957) is an American television and film actor. He is known for portraying Detective Tim Bayliss on the crime drama series Homicide: Life on the Street (1993–1999). Kyle_Ivan_Secor ( born May_31_,_1957 ) is an_American_television_and_film_actor .
